    "source_text": "我們旨在使友邦保險在科技應用方面領先全球，加強互聯互通，擴大規模和提升效率。更深入瞭解數據分析有助\n我們締造獨特和個人化的客戶體驗。切合和反映個人需求和生活方式的產品及服務，改變了大眾對人壽保險的看",
    "current_translation": "We aim to position AIA as a global leader in technology application, strengthen interconnectivity, expand scale and enhance efficiency. Deeper insights into data analytics enable us to create unique and personalized customer experiences. Products and services that align with and reflect individual needs and lifestyles have transformed public perceptions of life insurance."
  },
